Results of #SARSCoV2 #vaccine trial being discussed at today's #FDA adv committee mtg are now published in @NEJM. Two-dose regimen has 95% efficacy: 8 cases in vaccine arm, 162 cases in placebo arm, no serious adv events. 

🏆NO cases of #COVID19 in >1.5K Black pts in vaccine arm https://t.co/TM0JfJaxwM
